RTCCertificateStatsFingerprintAlgorithm.summary: The fingerprintAlgorithm property of the dictionary is a string containing the name of the hash function used to generate the value in the associated .
RTCCertificateStatsFingerprintAlgorithm.value: A string containing the name of the hash function used to create the fingerprint of the associated certificate.Allowed values are: "sha-1", "sha-224", "sha-256","sha-384", "sha-512", "md5", "md2". <!-- from [RFC4572, Section 5](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc4572#section-5) -->
